Create Area chart and Line chart Visualizations 12

Create Area chart and Line chart Visualizations

Crime Rate by DOW

Select  Area chart visual

Go to the Fields pane

Drag and drop DOW into Axis

Drag and drop CrimeRate into Value

Go to Format pane and turn On Data labels

Crime Rate by Hour Formal

Select Line chart Visual

Drag and drop Hour Formal into Axis

Drag and drop CrimeRate into Value

Go to Format pane and turn On Data labels
